name: Yoko Littner (Multiple Versions) [New cosplay version]
description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one. censored image prompt at bottom.

Space Yoko and Yamako are adults

A Lora trained on Yoko Littner, Yamako, and SpaceYoko. currently their three seperate Loras but I plan to merge them and Train each outfit for cosplay images.

(NEW - Yoko's clothing Lora weights are 0.8 - 1, if wanting to change hairstyle put her hair tags in the negative and lower weight, even then it is inconsistent

the clothing stags are the same as her character lora)

Weights 0.6 - 1 (1 should be fine unless you want to change outfit)

classic Yoko Littner: Yoko, 1girl, yoko_littner, red_hair, solo, breasts, bikini, flame_print, long_hair, hair_ornament, large_breasts, ponytail, yellow_eyes, gloves, striped_scarf, pink_legwear, hair_stick, skull_hair_ornament, flame_print, fingerless_gloves, belt.

Optional: elbow_gloves (don't know if it's better than gloves), sniper_rifle ( is quite bad, might be better on models with good guns), spiked_gloves (haven't tested), bikini_top_only (may help if it is genning a bikini bottom), jacket ( haven't tested much).

have gotten mixed results removing the Yoko Littner tag so i recommend keeping it to be safe, seems to like to gen her with one hand up for some reason.

Space Yoko: SpaceYoko, red_hair, long_hair, star_\(symbol\), large_breasts, yellow_eyes, ponytail, gloves, cleavage, hair_stick, strapless, tube_top, white_thighhighs/legwear.

optional: underboob (think it helps accuracy, but may mess with camera angle), jacket (not sure if this is actually tagged).

the captions on this weren't the greatest so will need to redo them.

Yamako (teacher): Yamako, teacher, long_hair, hair_down, red_hair, skirt, chalkboard, necktie, yellow_eyes, large_breasts, smile, side_slit, long_sleeves.

optional: glasses, pointer, ruler, chalk.

error on my part most of the images in the Space Yoko Lora aren't the version I uploaded which was 79, though the difference isn't much so I think I'll keep it.

the prompt for the censored image is: <lora:Yoko-NormalV1-000068:1.0>, Yoko, 1girl, breasts, yoko_littner, nipples, solo, smile, gloves, navel, scarf, hair_ornament, large_breasts, yellow_eyes, bikini, long_hair, fingerless_gloves, swimsuit, skull_hair_ornament, looking_at_viewer, white_background, striped_scarf, grin, simple_background, ponytail, bikini_top_only, bikini_pull, nipples

modelVersions.name: AIO - LoHa (Characters)
modelVersions.description:
A LoHa trained on the three versions, much more accurate and less bleed than the Lora.

requires the LoCon and Lycoris webui extensions. (changed the trigger words to prevent bleeding)

putting white_legwear for space yoko will result in her (whatever her lower clothes are called) turn into thighhighs, not using it will result in them 50/50 being correct and adding the cape tag will add her jacket. make sure you use the white_gloves tag, white_cape also seems to help

for classic yoko not sure I'm not sure if the yoko_littner tag is optional is helpful more than it is harmful (usually).

added the studded_belt tag and got rid of weapon tags besides sniper rifle, so it may be able to gen better. for classic yoko do not use pink_legwear us pink_thighighs, if it adds the star from space yoko to her thighhighs add star_\(symbol\) to the negative. flame_print is usually unnecessary and may result in fire/flames on her other clothing, her bikini should have the flames baked in. her skull ornament seems to not look great in this version not sure why. her gloves are also weird, you can either get them wrist or elbow, and you can make both of those fingerless, but you can't get one type of glove on either hand. for my next version I will bake in the clothing.

for Yamako her outfit looks much more accurate.
